        <h1>FixTestErl</h1>
        <p>FixTestErl is a system for automated testing and market simultion.
        It allows users to test positive and negative use-case scenarios within
        buy-side and sell-side applications, which speak FIX.
        FixTestErl supports cross session integration giving the ability 
        to complete robust testing across systems.
